    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The exterior has extensive rust damage on the rocker panels and frame, along with significant paint peeling and several large dents. Mechanically, the engine runs but requires immediate attention for several leaks and a failing transmission. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is being sold strictly as-is with no guarantees of roadworthiness.",
